### Complete Product Creation Workflow
### This file demonstrates the complete process of creating products with variants
### Execute requests in order and replace variables with returned IDs

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

###

### ============================================================
### STEP 1: Create Attributes
### ============================================================

### 1.1 Create Color Attribute
# @name createColorAttribute
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/attributes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Color",
  "description": "Product color options",
  "displayOrder": 1,
  "isActive": true
}

### 1.2 Create Storage Attribute
# @name createStorageAttribute
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/attributes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Storage",
  "description": "Storage capacity",
  "displayOrder": 2,
  "isActive": true
}

### ============================================================
### STEP 2: Create Attribute Values for Color
### ============================================================

### 2.1 Create Black Color Value
# @name createBlackValue
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/attribute-values
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attributeId": "{{createColorAttribute.response.body.id}}",
  "value": "Black",
  "displayOrder": 1,
  "isActive": true
}

### 2.2 Create White Color Value
# @name createWhiteValue
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/attribute-values
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

