### ============================================================
### STEP 5: Create Product Variants for iPhone 15 Pro
### ============================================================

### 5.1 iPhone 15 Pro - Black 128GB
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/variants
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "{{createIPhone15Pro.response.body.id}}",
  "sku": "IPHONE-15-PRO-BLK-128",
  "additionalPrice": 0,
  "stockQuantity": 50,
  "isActive": true,
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/images/iphone15pro-black.jpg",
  "attributeValueIds": [
    "{{createBlackValue.response.body.id}}",
    "{{create128GBValue.response.body.id}}"
  ]
}

### 5.2 iPhone 15 Pro - Black 256GB
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/variants
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
