### ============================================================
### STEP 7: Verify Created Data
### ============================================================

### Get All Products (should show 5 products)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get All Attributes (should show 2 attributes)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/attributes/all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get All Attribute Values (should show 9+ values)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/attribute-values/all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get All Product Variants (should show 9+ variants)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/variants/all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Specific Product with All Variants
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/{{createIPhone15Pro.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Color Attribute with Values
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/attributes/{{createColorAttribute.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
